    <h1>LG Appliance Repair — Los Angeles, Orange County &amp; Ventura County</h1>

    <p>Same Day Appliance Repair provides certified LG appliance repair across all three Southern California counties. Our technicians specialize exclusively in LG — dryers, washers, refrigerators, ranges, ovens, and dishwashers — and arrive typically within 1 to 1.5 hours of your call. The $65 diagnostic fee is waived when you proceed with the repair.</p>

